  <brief_title>Comparative Pain Control Between 0.2 or 0.3 Spinal Morphine and 0.25 or 0.5 % Bupivacaine for FNB After TKA</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparative Effect of 0.2 or 0.3 Spinal Morphine and 0.25 or 0.5 % Bupivacaine for Femoral Nerve Block After Total Knee Replacement</official_title>
