  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparative efficacy of 24 and 48 hours post operative pain control in single total knee
      replacement between intrathecal bupivacaine with 0.2 or 0.3 mg morphine together with 0.25 or
      0.5 % bupivacaine for single femoral nerve block
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
